'''独立公园'''（{{lang-he|גן העצמאות}}，''Gan HaAtzma'ut''）是以色列[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]的一个公园，四周是阿格隆街、[[乔治王街_(耶路撒冷)|乔治王街]]、希勒尔街和门纳什本以色列街<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gojerusalem.com/discover/item_125/Independence-Park-Gan-Haatzmaut |title=Independence Park (Gan Ha'atzmaut) |publisher=gojerusalem.com |access-date=2016-02-11 |archive-date=2013-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101024329/http://www.gojerusalem.com/discover/item_125/Independence-Park-Gan-Haatzmaut |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它是耶路撒冷第二大公园<ref>{{cite book |title=Jerusalem: The Mini Rough Guide |url=http://books.google.co.il/books?id=60ekWVd-Xu4C&pg=PA130&lpg=PA130&dq=%22Hillel+Street%22&source=bl&ots=iJGVzVPIen&sig=N-wb9fIylynxv7pZpBWUbsKFK9Q&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22Hillel%20Street%22&f=false |first=Daniel |last=Jacobs |page=130 |access-date=2016-02-11 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309224721/https://books.google.co.il/books?id=60ekWVd-Xu4C&pg=PA130&lpg=PA130&dq=%22Hillel+Street%22&source=bl&ots=iJGVzVPIen&sig=N-wb9fIylynxv7pZpBWUbsKFK9Q&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22Hillel%20Street%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fonerbooks.com/guide_25.htm |first=Morris |last=Rosenthal |title=Jerusalem Parks - Gan for Dog Owners |year=2006 |access-date=2016-02-11 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093018/http://www.fonerbooks.com/guide_25.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该公园有狮子洞穴。犹太人，穆斯林和基督教的传说都认为，他们信徒的遗体被埋葬在那里，上帝派[[狮子|狮子]]在那里守卫死人<ref name=allabout>{{cite web |url=http://allaboutjerusalem.com/tour/2000-years-old-pool-cemetery-cave-more?page=16 |first=Ron |last=Peled |title=2,000 Years Old Pool, Cemetery, Cave & more... |accessdate=2016-02-11 |archive-date=2013-01-17 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130117054902/http://allaboutjerusalem.com/tour/2000-years-old-pool-cemetery-cave-more?page=16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。犹太人的传统规定，被[[塞琉古帝国|塞琉古帝国]]希腊人所啥的犹太人葬在那里。穆斯林认为真主将遗体从附近墓地转移到该洞以逃离火灾。[[基督徒|基督徒]]相信 洞穴里埋葬的是614年波斯[[萨珊王朝|萨珊王朝]]围攻耶路撒冷时修士们的遗体。<ref name=allabout />。

该公园也是在耶路撒冷同性恋活跃的地区之一，已成为许多LGBT活动的焦点，包括每年的同性恋游行<ref name=itravel>{{cite web|url=http://www.itraveljerusalem.com/BusinessAbout.aspx?id=197|title=Independence Park|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130127194004/http://www.itraveljerusalem.com/BusinessAbout.aspx?id=197|archivedate=2013-01-27}}</ref>。

